name: SpaceLaunches
0:
”Alexa, open space launches”
”Give me the flight number of the upcoming launch”
”Give me all the information about the latest launch”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: space launches
des:
This skill provides information like the flight number, the crew members, the name of flight or further details for the latest launch or an upcoming launch of SpaceX flights. 

I am a 9-year-old and this is my first Alexa skill. This skill was developed as a part of North South Foundation's Alexa programming course team project.

I am not affiliated with SpaceX in any way. This is a fun skill that I wrote which tells people information about SpaceX flights. I hope people will enjoy this.

This skill extracts information from the publicly available api below-
1. https://api.spacexdata.com/v4/launches/latest
2. https://api.spacexdata.com/v4/launches/upcoming
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
